{"type": "article", "id": 27329, "title": "多功能的星空时钟", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-26T06:58:34Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 101, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702162504zRUlWifb3ypeVAL7.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>居住在高楼林立的大都市，你可能很少见到繁星点点的夜空了，设计师 Jay Hyun Kim 打算将星星和常用的生活工具结合在一起：他设计的这款 Cosmos 既是一盏氛围灯，同时还是一个时钟和扬声器。Cosmos 的表面是一张星座图，详细地还原了北半球所有可见的星座，一大一小的两个圆圈则分别表示了时针和分针。通过蓝牙连接上手机后你可以播放自己喜欢的音乐或是调整它的灯光颜色。Cosmos 将会在 Kickstarter 上展开众筹，如果你有兴趣的话可以关注它的<a href=\"http://www.jayhyunkim.com/#/cosmos/\">产品页面</a>。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162501GsyX6hd0Qnx4KAFT.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.55142857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162502cWtRrdNjLzOqJ4s2.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56285714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162503Ork4vYup0WMF5gBe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56285714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162503OtfswRUE3K8GN9n5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69904762\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}